N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 102.15 - Review of board action

State Regulations

Any determination of the board with reference to the
issuance, denial, modification or revocation of a certificate of eligibility, or any renewal or extension thereof, shall be reviewable under article 78 of
the Civil Practice Law and Rules. Notes
